name: Liberty Lite
shortDescription: A (lite) general purpose jailbreak detection bypass patch. Use the Liberty entry in the Settings app to block (most) apps from detecting your jailbreak. Disabling Substrate/Substitute is not supported, so certain apps (PayPal, HSBC HK) will still be problematic.
author: Ryley Angus
